description: With a mission to make mouths happy quick, lick by lick, Chris & Katy are grinnin’ and spinnin’  through the Twin Cities, spreading jollies with their delicious Ice Lollies. Using fresh, all-natural ingredients, FrioFrio offers the most lickable, pickable, fruity frozen treats on a stick. Strawberry Balsamic Basil, Avocado Lime, Thai Boba Iced Tea, and so much more. With gluten & dairy-free options galore, it’s no wonder that these are the refreshing treats that Minnesotans adore. Go to town on these Ice Lollies and turn that frown upside down with FrioFrio!
name: FrioFrio
